       var unit = 'shares';

	function getDownload() {
		var e = document.getElementById('select');
		if (e.value == '')
			return;
		var filename = e.value;
		if (unit != 'shares')
			filename += unit;
		filename += '.csv';

		window.open(url);

	function printEquitiesGrid(val) {

	{

	{

	function StopMarketVol() {
		clearTimeout(window.HomePageTimers['DailyVolumeTimer']);
	}

	function setUnits(val) {
		var tab1 = 'tabshares';
		var tab2 = 'tabtrades';
		var tab3 = 'tabdollarVol';
		var equitiesLabel = 'equitiesLabel';
		var e = document.getElementById(tab1);
		e.className = 'tabsInternal';
		e = document.getElementById(tab2);
		e.className = 'tabsInternal';
		e = document.getElementById(tab3);
		e.className = 'tabsInternal';
		e = document.getElementById('tab' + val);
		e.className = 'tabsInternal tabsInternalClicked';
		e = document.getElementById(equitiesLabel);
		if (val == 'shares')
			e.innerHTML = 'Volume';
		if (val == 'trades')
			e.innerHTML = 'Trades';
		if (val == 'dollarVol')
			e.innerHTML = 'Dollar Volume';
      unit = val;
		StopMarketVol();
		GetMarketVol();
    }

	function setDefaultUnits() {
        setCookie('MarketShareDefaultUnits',unit, 365);
    }

    function GetMarketVol() {

        var s;
        var s2;
		var mdy = $.datepicker.formatDate('mm/dd/yy',dataDate);

        s2 = 'equitiesTab';
        var e = document.getElementById(s2);
        if (e !=  null) e.innerHTML = "updating....";
		s2 = 'optionsTab';
        e = document.getElementById(s2);
        if (e !=  null) e.innerHTML = "updating....";
        Server.BL_MarketShare.GetUpdateMarkup(cb_GetUpdateMarkup, 'DESKTOP', unit, mdy);
		Server.BL_MarketShare.GetOptionsUpdateMarkup(cb_GetOptionsUpdateMarkup, 'DESKTOP');

        window.HomePageTimers['DailyVolumeTimer'] = setTimeout('GetMarketVol()', 1000*60);

    }

    function cb_GetUpdateMarkup(r, e){
        if (e) return alert(e.message);
		var a = r.split('|');
        var d = document.getElementById('equitiesTab');
        if (d != null)
            d.innerHTML = a[1];
		d = document.getElementById('equitiesTs');
        if (d != null)
            d.innerHTML = a[0];

    }

	function cb_GetOptionsUpdateMarkup(r, e){
        if (e) return alert(e.message);
		var a = r.split('|');
        var d = document.getElementById('optionsTab');
        if (d != null)
            d.innerHTML = a[1];
		d = document.getElementById('optionsTs');
        if (d != null)
            d.innerHTML = a[0];

    }

	var availableDates = [];

function initAvailableDates() {
	var d = $.datepicker.formatDate('mm/dd/yy',new Date());
	availableDates.push(d);
	var x = Server.BL_MarketShare.GetMarketVolumeDates();
	var i;
	var xx;
	for (i = 0; i < x.length; i++)
	{
		xx = x[i];
		availableDates.push(xx.ValidDate);
	}
}

function available(date) {
  mdy = $.datepicker.formatDate('mm/dd/yy',date);
  if ($.inArray(mdy, availableDates) >= 0) {
    return [true,"","Choose"];
  } else {
    return [false,"","Invalid Date"];
  }
}

function onDateSelect(dateText, inst)
{
	dataDate = new Date(dateText);
	GetMarketVol();
}
function setDatePicker() {
  $('#chooseDate').datepicker({
  ampm: true,
  showOn: "both",
  buttonImage: "/images/calendar_16x16.gif",
  buttonImageOnly: true,
  buttonText: "Choose another date",
  beforeShowDay: available,
  onSelect: onDateSelect
  });
}

$(function(){
    document.getElementById('chooseDate').value = $.datepicker.formatDate('mm/dd/yy',dataDate);
    setDatePicker();
	initAvailableDates();
	var myUnit = getCookie('MarketShareDefaultUnits');
	if (myUnit == null || myUnit == '')
		myUnit = 'shares';
	window.HomePageTimers= new Object();
	window.HomePageTimers.DailyVolumeTimer = null;
	setUnits(myUnit);
});
